Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.24,0:22:31.68,ED-RO,,0,0,0,,{\fade(230,230)\blur20}{\i0}Kodoku mo shiranu trickster{\i}
Comment: 0,0:21:27.28,0:21:32.31,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,===ED-CN===
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.28,0:21:32.31,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fade(230,230)\blur20}{\i0}看見誰都無法看見的夢{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.42,0:21:37.79,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fade(230,230)\blur20}{\i0}捨棄所有不需要的事物{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.89,0:21:41.09,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fade(230,230)\blur20}{\i0}無法割捨的感情{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.19,0:21:46.63,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fade(230,230)\blur20}{\i0}深藏在我的心裏{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.73,0:21:53.10,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fade(230,230)\blur20}{\i0}依然處在現實與理想的夾縫中{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.20,0:21:58.30,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fade(230,230)\blur20}{\i0}即使犧牲的枷鎖 栓住我的腳{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.41,0:22:03.44,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fade(230,230)\blur20}{\i0}無法壓抑滿腔的衝動{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.55,0:22:10.35,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fade(230,230)\blur20}{\i0}因為我有一顆強烈追求的心{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.32,0:22:16.09,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fade(230,230)\blur20}{\i0}虛偽 恐懼 虛飾 憂愁{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.19,0:22:21.63,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fade(230,230)\blur20}{\i0}面對各種負面情緒{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.73,0:22:27.14,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fade(230,230)\blur20}{\i0}我也不會弱到被擊垮{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.24,0:22:31.68,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fade(230,230)\blur20}{\i0}不知孤獨為何物 Trickster{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.49,0:22:39.75,Sub,,0,0,0,,要是這個女人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.86,0:22:42.45,Sub,,0,0,0,,搶在我之前告訴警方的話...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.43,0:22:44.56,Sub,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.67,0:22:48.90,Sub,,0,0,0,,似乎連死神之外的神 也是站在我這邊的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.00,0:22:51.90,Sub,,0,0,0,,下一回 破綻
